1. *Shvati* da se sadašnjost može promeniti. (Understand that the present can be changed.)

2. Moraš da *shvatite* da je ovo važno. (You must understand that this is important.)

3. *Shvatila* sam da je ovo problem. (I realized that this was a problem.)

4. On je *shvatio* da nije ispravno. (He understood that it was not correct.)

5. *Shvatili* smo da je to veoma teško. (We realized that it was very difficult.)